rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0001
rows.name: Finally, we're off to the capital.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0003
rows.name:
I wonder what the capital's like.
I'm really excited, Shin!

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0004
rows.name:
I don't think it's anything
to get that excited over.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0005
rows.name: I know what we're here for.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0006
rows.name:
But if we get some free time,
I'd like to have some fun and go
clothes shopping with Laura-sama.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0007
rows.name: I'm not trying to criticize you.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0008
rows.name:
That's something only you
can do with her, Kasumi.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0009
rows.name:
If you get the chance,
you should enjoy yourselves.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0011
rows.name:
When we're shopping,
please come along as our bag carrier.

rows.label: campfev11_500_110_msg0012
rows.name: How did it come to this...
